The paper deals with formalisation and analysis of data dependencies between components, which is a key concern in software engineering (cs.SE). The use of Isabelle/HOL+Isar suggests a focus on programming languages and formal methods (cs.PL). The paper also discusses system structure and model checking, which are topics in logic (cs.LO) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the analysis of system components and properties suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
